Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:47.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}在这世界上不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:52.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}打上无尽的刻印的
