Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:03.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘载着不变的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:08.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}去打开闭锁的门扉吧
