Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:05.64,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.89,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去救我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.27,Junko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给消防队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.44,Junko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人别擅自妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.31,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我才行…
