Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:17.94,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:34.62,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:40.96,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  无论多少次都胜不了那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:51.84,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复的话  每次轮回都会增加小圆的因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.18,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)}到头来我做的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.17,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:30.22,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了  小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.34,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:46.61,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆…
